Veteran actress and movie producer, Toyin Adewale has taken to social media to celebrate her son, Mayorkun as he turns a new age today. In a post sighted on her Instagram page, the proud mother shared photos of Mayorkun as she gushed over him and wished him a happy birthday. She prayed for the blessings of God to multiply on his life as he continues on his journey. See post below View this post on Instagram A post shared by TOYIN ADEWALE (@officialtoyinadewale)